        (24657, 'Franco Zeffirelli', '1923-02-12', 'From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.  Franco Zeffirelli, KBE (Hon),  (born 12 February 1923) is an Italian film director and producer of films and television and opera director and designer. He has also been a politician (The People of Freedom).

