Description above from the Wikipedia article María Casares, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'A Coruña, Galicia, Spain', 1, '/vH9Tif8ZaK8yXzVusPdhjLpr4FQ.jpg'),
