        (26930, 'Amy Morton', '1958-01-01', 'Amy Morton (born January 1, 1958) is an American actress and director, best known for her work in theatre. She was nominated two times for a Tony Award for Best Actress in a Play for her performances in August: Osage County and Who''s Afraid of Virginia Woolf?. She is currently starring as Sergeant Trudy Platt in the NBC drama series Chicago P.D.', 'Oak Park - Illinois - USA', 1, '/cf0V37Bw9BX2jlBCxrVETz0jkcl.jpg'),
