        (27913, 'June Tripp', '1901-06-11', 'June Tripp, who sometimes professionally went by solely the name June, was an English stage and film actress, best known for portraying the character Daisy in the 1927 Alfred Hitchcock Silent film The Lodger: A Story of the London Fog. She became an American citizen in 1951.', 'England', 1, NULL),
