She later starred as Barbara Marx in The Night We Called It a Day (2003), and has appeared on the television series Nip/Tuck, Raising Hope, and Hawaii Five-0. After acting on stage in London, in 2003 she made her Broadway debut in a revival of the musical Chicago, receiving celebratory reviews that made it a box office success.', 'Manhattan, New York City, New York, USA', 1, '/rdRjFsPQDQqPE8JlDQcuT5JDpED.jpg'),
