        (34376, 'Nobuo Kaneko', '1923-03-27', 'Nobuo Kaneko (金子信雄 Kaneko Nobuo, 27 March 1923 – 20 January 1995) was a Japanese actor. He appeared in more than 200 films between 1950 and 1993. He was a versatile character actor, playing roles ranging from comedic buffoons to hardened yakuza bosses.', 'Taito, Tokyo, Japan', 1, '/iKcZ0rtO5sCfOSEBvyAdCk68EzY.jpg'),
