        (34842, 'Tony Amendola', '1944-08-24', 'From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.

Tony Amendola is an American actor who is best known for playing the Jaffa masterBra''tac in Stargate SG-1. Amendola is also known for his recurring role as revolutionary leader Edouard Kagame of Liber8 in the television show Continuum. He currently is a minor character on ABC''sOnce Upon a Time as Pinocchio''s creator/father, Geppetto.', 'New Haven - Connecticut - USA', 3, '/wjft9mXp65SfSo2g3pnLxZUOEzG.jpg'),
