        (35875, 'Nadine Van der Velde', '1962-05-14', 'Nadine was born in Toronto, Ontario, Canada. She is fluent in French. She made her film debut in 1983 in the film Private School. She later starred in the 1986 comedy horror Critters and 1987 film Munchies. Her acting credits include several TV series including: Silver Spoons, Otherworld, The New Alfred Hitchcock Presents and JAG.  -From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia', '	Toronto, Ontario, Canada', 1, '/lMikuFbSdy4fAdlI0zdHApuOzfd.jpg'),
