        (36039, 'Adrian Zmed', '1954-03-04', 'Adrian Zmed was born in Chicago on March 14, 1954, the son of George Zmed, a Romanian Orthodox priest, and his wife, Persida. He is an actor, known for T.J. Hooker (1982), Bachelor Party (1984) and  Grease 2 (1982). He has been married to Lyssa Lynne since October 5,  2012. He was previously married to Barbara Fitzner and Susan Wood.

